Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time for cases to move from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are resubmitted
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to cases without it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING does not occur

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time it takes for a case to be closed after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time for a case to be reopened after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by MISSING and the end of the case

Name: Average time to reach 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' from the start of the case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' compared to those with 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by MISSING' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
